title: please help a student to complete her csp
selftext:

Please take 5 minutes to complete this survey. This was given by my college as a community service project. I don't have much connections or network irl I need atleast 100 responses to analyze and get credits. This is the only place I can think about to get responses. Thanks in advance. (This isn't fake I am posting this on as many subs as possible for maximum visibility). And you don't need to give your real name, I made the name question optional.
